Shop for collegeAs a college freshman or an upperclassman, going away to college is an exciting time in your life. Whether you are living at a college dorm room or an off-campus apartment, you will need some basics to furnish your place. We offer a large assortment of college bedding (including dorm room Twin XL sheets), dorm furniture, dorm room kits, bathroom necessities, storage solutions, and dorm room decorations to make your dorm room comfortable. At our Shop for College online site, find decorating ideas and a checklist of everything you need to furnish a dorm room. Check out our services—Pack & Hold®, our free service that lets you shop at your local store and pick up at a store near your school and College Registry where you can create, manage and share your registry with family and friends. At Bed Bath & Beyond we make shopping for college easy, convenient and fun.  




