Cited Cases






WORLDWIDE HOME PRODUCTS, INC., Plaintiff,
v.
BED, BATH AND BEYOND, INC. et al., Defendants.


United States District Court, S.D. New York.
September 30, 2014.








Attorney(s) appearing for the Case
Worldwide Home Products, Inc., Plaintiff, represented by  Gail Ellen Podolsky , Carlton Fields, P.A. &  Vitaly David Rivkin , Carlton Fields Jorden Burt, P.A..
Time, Inc., Defendant, represented by  Edward F O'Connor , The Eclipse Group LLP,  Lewis Emery Hudnell, III , Colvin Hudnell LLP &  Uleses Columbus Henderson , The Edelsteins, Faegenburg & Brown.
Bed, Bath and Beyond Inc., Defendant, represented by  Edward F O'Connor , The Eclipse Group LLP,  Lewis Emery Hudnell, III , Colvin Hudnell LLP &  Uleses Columbus Henderson , The Edelsteins, Faegenburg & Brown.
Cohesion Products Inc., Defendant, represented by  Edward F O'Connor , The Eclipse Group LLP,  Lewis Emery Hudnell, III , Colvin Hudnell LLP &  Uleses Columbus Henderson , The Edelsteins, Faegenburg & Brown.
Sherry Hanson, Defendant, represented by  Edward F O'Connor , The Eclipse Group LLP,  Lewis Emery Hudnell, III , Colvin Hudnell LLP &  Uleses Columbus Henderson , The Edelsteins, Faegenburg & Brown.
